ttps://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movies/news/Siddharth-teams-up-with-Kappal-director-for-an-action-comedy/articleshow/52554223.cms|title=Siddharth teams up with Kappal director for an action comedy - Times of India|website=The Times of India}}</ref> called his antagonistic role \"quirky\" and a \"crazy, interesting\" one.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-16/vamsi-krishna-is-the-quirky-baddie-in-siddharths-shaitan-ka-bachcha.html|title=Vamsi Krishna is the quirky baddie in Siddharth's Shaitan Ka Bachcha|date=1 August 2016|website=Behindwoods}}</ref> [[Santhosh Narayanan]] joined the team to compose the film's music, while cinematography was announced to be handled by [[Aravinnd Singh]] and editing by [[Anthony (film editor)|Anthony]]. The film began production during June 2016, while [[Raashi Khanna]] was announced as the film's lead actress in September 2016.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://silverscreen.in/news/raashi-khanna-will-make-tamil-debut-siddharths-saithaan-ka-bachcha/|title=Raashi Khanna Will Make Her Tamil Debut With Siddharth\u2019s Saithaan Ka Bachcha|date=22 September 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-16/santosh-narayanan-part-of-siddharths-shaitan-ki-bachcha.html|title=Santosh Narayanan part of Siddharth's Shaitan Ki Bachcha|date=7 June 2016|website=Behindwoods}}</ref>\n\nDue to the film's delay, Raashi Khanna went on to act in other Tamil films while Siddharth and Karthik went on to do other film called ''Takkar''.<ref>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movies/news/siddharth-teams-up-with-karthik-g-krish-again/articleshow/72166851.cms</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|2}}\n\n== External links ==\n*{{IMDb title|7943200}}\n\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n[[Category:Upcoming Tamil-language films]]\n[[Category:Indian action comedy films]]\n[[Category:Films scored by Santhosh Narayanan]]\n[[Category:Unreleased Tamil-language films]]